    <h1>Receive Plasma Blood</h1>
    <h4>Need a plasma blood donor? we are here for you. Complete the registeration process to add yourself to the lis.</h4>
    <div class="boxes">
    <div class="card" style="width: 40rem;">
    <img class="card-img-top" src="https://source.unsplash.com/1400x400/?blood donation" alt="Card image cap">
    <div class="card-body">
    <form action="/receiveplasmablood" method="post">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>First Name</label>
      <input type="text"  class="form-control" placeholder="First name" name="FirstName">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>Last Name</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Last name" name="LastName">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>Email ID</label>
      <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email ID" name="EmailID">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>Mobile Number</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Mobile Number" name="MobileNo">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>Address</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Address" name="Address">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>City</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="City" name="City">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>State</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="State" name="State">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>Date of Birth</label>
      <input type="Date" class="form-control" placeholder="Date of Birth" name="DOB">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>Age</label>
      <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="Age" name="Age">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>Blood Group</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Blood Group" name="BloodGroup">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <label>Sex</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Sex" name="Sex">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>Height(in cm)</label>
      <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="Height" name="Height">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <label>Weight(in Kg)</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Weight" name="Weight">
    </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="form-group">
    <div class="form-check">
      <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="gridCheck">
      <label class="form-check-label" for="gridCheck">
      |I hearby agree that all the information entered is true
      </label>
    </div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <p class="card-text">
    |Every blood donor is a lifesaver
    </p>
